      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must be conducted on the same device geometry and within the same operating envelope (flow rate, speed) as the COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry, which is identical to the device geometry used in the COU simulations. The five operating points span the full clinical operating envelope specified in the COU. Required level 2 is met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
