      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence of residuals to at least 1e-5 for all transport equations; mass imbalance < 0.1%.",
      "rationale": "All simulations were run to residual convergence of 1e-6 for continuity and momentum equations. Global mass imbalance was below 0.05% in all cases. Required level 1 is satisfied."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Evidence of independent review of simulation setup, boundary conditions, and post-processing scripts by a qualified analyst not involved in the primary simulation work.",
      "rationale": "An independent senior CFD analyst reviewed all boundary condition specifications, turbulence model selections, and post-processing scripts prior to final result extraction. Review comments were documented and resolved. Required level 1 is met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
